data.description:
This Beautiful Gem is located in Harder Hall across from Little Lake Jackson (some views). This home has been very well maintained. Has a screened in pool, Property has an Olive and Leeche tree. The kitchen has been completely updated, New A/C, Water Heater, New pool pump system (This year). New Roof in 2018. Septic was pumped in 2019. Currently using garage as workout area. It can be converted back to the 2 car garage. If your a golfer you will love this home as you can see the 3rd hole from back yard and just minutes away from playing at Harder Hall or Sebring Municipal Golf Course.
"MORE PHOTOS COMING SOON!!"
